metadata.title: Forum Novelties M38028 Morbid Enterprises Tree Hugger Witch Prop, One Size
features: Perfect for Halloween and costume parties, cosplay and convention events, theme parties, theatrical productions or every day dress up!
description: You'll have the spookiest house on the block this Halloween when you buy the Tree Hugging Witch Prop! This creepy prop features a green-skinned witch with black and purple tattered robes on. Tie her up to a tree with the attached ropes, and it will seem like you've caught an evil witch and are now keeping her prisoner! Buy your witch tree prop today, and then scan our site for more spooky Halloween decorations.
